title: Ten Years After - The Anthology 1967-1971 (2002, 2CD) [flac]
description:
Ten Years After - The Anthology 1967-1971 (2002, 2CD) [flac]

Few band's compilations really capture most of the great moments of the band's history, but this one really is the exception. I've got all the vinyl LPs (worn out and scratched) but this 2CD collection hits all the high notes. A =GREAT= rock'n'roll band with the blistering-fast fingers of Alvin Lee on guitar, this is a must-have for all rock'n'roll fans.
